parameters: Why did I even become a Pony Celes...

If I hadn't accepted that request, I wouldn't have ended up like
this...
I wonder what will happen if I'm not here...
Will everyone be killed by Zaidargg...?
Will I lose all the people important to me...?
No... I don't want that at all!!
The voice calling me... It's \n[6]'s voice...
I've always wanted to hear this voice...

A voice that stays by my side and gives me courage... That's why I was
able to keep going...
フラッシュバックを入れる
Yui: "...I lost to Dargnoir... in front of everyone..."

\n[6]: "...Yui, you've done enough. You fought against Zaidargg all by
yourself. Now it's time to rest and return to a normal life."
Polka: "Yui-chan, you've already done enough. Leave the rest to me."
Polka: "I'll seal Dargnoir again and put an end to everything."
Yui: "...You must be out of power by now, right, Polka?"
Yui: "Even if you lie, I know that much."
Polka: "You've done enough. So let's not worry about Zaidargg anymore."
Yui: "I'm the only one who can stop Zaidargg."
\n[6]: "Stop it! I won't let Yui go through that again--"

Yui: "Polka! You have a spell that can seal Dargnoir, right? Teach it
to me!"

Polka: "Holy Resurrection is an ultimate spell that converts life into
power to activate."

Polka: "If you use it, you will surely die. I can't let you take on
that role, no matter what."

Yui: "What are you saying now! Wasn't it you, Polka, who said you
wanted me to defeat Zaidargg...?"

Polka: "I intended to finish it myself in the end. But when it
mattered most, I failed..."

Polka: "You're right, I don't have any power left. I'm sorry, Yui-
chan... It's all my responsibility..."
Yui: "I don't want to hear that! Just teach me the spell!"

\n[6]: "It's a promise between me and her. That's why Polka can't
teach the spell to Yui."
